### HTTP API Quick Reference

|  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Method | Path | Request Body | Success Response |
| GET | /api/models/list | — | { "models": [{name, display\_name, size\_mb, languages, downloaded, active}] } |
| GET | /api/models/status | — | { "active\_model", "model\_path", "dimensions" } |
| POST | /api/models/download | { "model\_name": "..." } | { "success": true, "status": "downloading" } |
| POST | /api/models/switch | { "model\_name": "..." } | { "success": true, "active\_model": "..." } |

